WarmDirt - The Greenhouse Box Temperature Controller

Here's a greenhouse box temperature controller for winter growing.

Requirements
    Sensors
        Temperature 
            Heated dirt
            Potted dirt
            Box interior air
            Box exterior air
        Humidity 
            Box Interior
        Ambient light
        Lid closed switch
        Heater current monitor

    Control
        Heater
        DC Motor

    Communication
        XBEE

    Framework
        Arduino compatible using ATMEGA328P
        

ATMEGA328P pin mapping

Pin Port    Description
1   PD3     PCINT19 OC2B    INT1
2   PD4     PCINT20 XCK     T0 
3   GND
4   VCC
5   GND
6   VCC
7   PB6     PCINT6  XTAL1   TOSC1 
8   PB7     PCINT7  XTAL2   TOSC2 

9   PD5     PCINT21 OC0B    T1
10  PD6     PCINT22 OC0A    AIN0
11  PD7     PCINT23         AIN1
12  PB0     PCINT0  CLKO    ICP1
13  PB1     PCINT1  OC1A
14  PB2     PCINT2  OC1B    SS
15  PB3     PCINT3  OC2A    MOSI
16  PB4     PCINT4          MISO

17  PB5     PCINT5          SCK
18  AVCC
19  ADC6
20  AREF
21  GND
22  ADC7
23  PC0     PCINT8  ADC0
24  PC1     PCINT9  ADC1

25  PC2     PCINT10 ADC2
26  PC3     PCINT11 ADC3
27  PC4     PCINT12 ADC4    SDA
28  PC5     PCINT13 ADC5    SCL
29  PC6     PCINT14         RESET
30  PD0     PCINT16         RXD
31  PD1     PCINT17         TXD
32  PD2     PCINT18         INT0


